Modelling frailty in area mortality.

Congdon P(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Geography, Queen Mary and Westfield College, London, U.K.

This paper investigates the impact on area life tables of the specification of 
unobserved frailty. Frailty specification may affect both the regression effects 
of area and individual level covariates, and lead to changes in the value of 
